high_descs: Pick up the soap in the tub.
Bring the soap to the sink on the left.
Wet the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the soap to the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: turn around and walk forwards over to the bathroom tub
grab the soap out of the tub
turn around and walk to the far end of the kitchen sink
place the soap inside the sink, rinse off the soap, and then pick it back up
turn around and walk forwards over to the toilet
place the soap on top of the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place rinsed soap on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and go right, toward the sink, then turn right toward the tub.
Take the bar of soap from the tub.
Turn around, go toward the sink past the other sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn around, go to the toilet in front of you.
Place the bar of soap to the left of the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
